Do i think terrorism can be stopped? No. Ever heard the term..&quot;Where there is a will...there is a way&quot;?<BR>
We can pray for a world where we can be free to have our own opinions...and not suffer because of it. But to kill people because you feel you are right and they are wrong? <BR>
The United States has a right to defend itself..as well the rest of the world does as well. I am a citizen of the USA and even those that think the USA got what it deserved, I will heal you when you are at one bubble of life...I will buff you to keep you alive, I will summon food for you when you are hungry..because despite our differences, our opinions, our beliefs...we are both one kind...humankind.<BR>
<BR>
